title.narrative: CTP USAID - Skoll Innovative Investment Alliance

description.narrative: USAID and Skoll will make 6 to 10 co-investments in high impact social entrepreneurs to help take their models to scale, effect systems change, and more rigorously measure their impact.

participating-org.narrative: USAID redacted this field in accordance with the exceptions outlined in the Foreign Aid Transparency and Accountability Act of 2016.
